  m_Text: '<b><size="15"><color="#FFFFFF55">CONTROLS</color></size></b>

    <b>WASD:</b>
    Move

    <b>Space:</b> Jump

    <b>E:</b> Interact / Pick Up

    <b>H:</b>
    Toggle HNS ON/OFF

    <b>1 / 2 / 3 / 4:</b> Toggle Features ON/OFF

    <b>5
    / 6:</b> Toggle Radar/Minimap MODE

    <b>7:</b> Toggle Custom Minimap LAYER

    <b>X
    / C:</b> Zoom Radar -/+

    <b>V / B:</b> Offscreen Border -/+

    <b>N / M:</b>
    Minimap Zoom -/+'
